Really enjoyed this meal. Everything we tried was delicious and unique! I would give between 4-5 stars overall. We sat downstairs in a curved booth so it was more private, decor was nice and service good. My favorite dish was the eggplant curry and a pomelo salad appetizer. Flavors were fantastic!

Most excellent food!
